"title": "8315: orthodoxy, in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8315: orthodoxy, in ot",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The acceptance of God's revelation of himself to his people that should lead to worship and obedience.</p>\n<h2>Foundational truths about Israel's God</h2>\n<h3>God is one</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4\">DEU 6:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God is unique</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:39\">DEU 4:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:35\">DEU 4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:9\">PSA 97:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:6-Isa44:8\">ISA 44:6–44:8</a></p>\n<h3>God is self-existent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:14\">EXO 3:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God is the Creator</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4\">JOB 38:4</a></p>\n<h3>God will not tolerate rivals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:3-Exod20:6\">EXO 20:3–20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:7-Deut5:8\">DEU 5:7–5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:19-Deut8:20\">DEU 8:19–8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:6-Deut13:8\">DEU 13:6–13:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">ISA 42:8</a></p>\n<h3>God commands universal worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:9-Ps86:10\">PSA 86:9–86:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:21\">ISA 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:20-Zech8:22\">ZEC 8:20–8:22</a></p>\n<h2>Right belief is passed on through the community of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:4\">PSA 145:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:24-Exod12:27\">EXO 12:24–12:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:8\">DEU 6:6–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:20-Deut6:25\">DEU 6:20–6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:20-Josh4:24\">JOS 4:20–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:2-Ps78:6\">PSA 78:2–78:6</a></p>\n<h2>Right belief demands right practice</h2>\n<h3>Reverent fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Worship</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:4-Deut12:7\">DEU 12:4–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:35-2Kgs17:39\">2KI 17:35–17:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:28-1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:28–16:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:7-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:7–96:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6-Ps95:7\">PSA 95:6–95:7</a></p>\n<h3>Observance of festivals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:1-Deut16:2\">DEU 16:1–16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:9-Deut16:17\">DEU 16:9–16:17</a></p>\n<h3>Offering acceptable sacrifices</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:2-Lev1:4\">LEV 1:2–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:5-Lev5:6\">LEV 5:5–5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:7-Mal1:8\">MAL 1:7–1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness to the covenant</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:9-Deut29:15\">DEU 29:9–29:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:10\">PSA 25:10</a></p>\n<h3>Devotion to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:1\">DEU 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:19\">1CH 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:23\">PSA 31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a></p>\n<h3>Trust in God's faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:5\">PSA 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3-Ps37:5\">PSA 37:3–37:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:9-Ps115:11\">PSA 115:9–115:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89-Ps119:93\">PSA 119:89–119:93</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:32\">DEU 5:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:3\">DEU 6:1–6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16-Deut26:19\">DEU 26:16–26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:21\">ISA 30:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:21-Jer7:23\">JER 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Justice in society</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:3\">PSA 106:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:11–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a></p>\n<h2>Walking in God's ways</h2>\n<h3>God's ways are right</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:29\">PRO 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>Walking in God's ways brings his blessing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:33\">DEU 5:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:9\">DEU 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:19-Deut30:20\">DEU 30:19–30:20</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of kings who walked in God's ways</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:22\">2SA 22:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:21\">PSA 18:21</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:2-2Chr14:4\">2CH 14:2–14:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11-1Kgs15:12\">1KI 15:11–15:12</a> <em>Asa</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:3-2Chr17:6\">2CH 17:3–17:6</a> <em>Jehoshaphat</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:4\">2CH 26:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:3\">2KI 15:3</a> <em>Uzziah (and Amaziah)</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:2\">2CH 29:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:3\">2KI 18:3</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:2\">2CH 34:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:2\">2KI 22:2</a> <em>Josiah</em></p>",
